OL,5,
OL,6,CG1967FOur World - the first live,
OL,7,Finternational, satellite television
OL,8,Fproduction - airs on BBC One.
OL,9,
OL,10,FRadio Times: "The European Broadcasting
OL,11,FUnion, in association with the
OL,12,Ftelevision services of eighteen
OL,13,Fnations, presents Our World.
OL,14,
OL,15,F"This evening in Europe, this afternoon
OL,16,Fin America, tomorrow in Japan, live
OL,17,Ftelevision circles the globe for the
OL,18,Ffirst time ever, linking five
OL,19,Fcontinents and bringing man
OL,20,Fface-to-face with mankind in places as
OL,21,Ffar apart as Canberra and Cape Kennedy,
OL,22,FMoscow and Montreal, Samarkand and
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
