OL,6,CG2005FThe final episode of Balamory
OL,7,F(original run) airs on CBeebies.
OL,8,
OL,9,FHowever, the final episode to be made
OL,10,Fwas Seeking Santa which was made at the
OL,11,Fbeginning of 2005 in Glasgow and
OL,12,FFinland. This episode went straight to
OL,13,Fvideo and has never been shown on
OL,14,FBritish TV.
OL,15,
OL,16,FThe programme was revived in 2026.
